title: BBC Life In Cold Blood 5of5 Armoured Giants XviD AC3
description:
Part 5 - Armoured Giants 
The world of the armoured creature is equally fascinating and bizarre. Galapagos giant tortoises solve the problem of making love in a suit of armour; a heated sea turtle orgy leaves females in mortal danger and we witness the explosive arrival of a baby pig-nosed turtle. Giant saltwater crocodiles crowd a flooded river-run to fish for mullet and a caiman leads her brood in a touching trek to a communal creche.
